---------------------------------------------
Glaive with GreatStrike - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Glaive-GreatStrike AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Great Strike - Glaive&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a **Great Strike** Glaive attack*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d10!cf<4cs>10 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[1d10!cf<0cs>100 [Great Strike]]] [Great Strike] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods]]] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] + $[[1]] Slashing &#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[2]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[4]] Slashing + $[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[3]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
Glaive-GreatStrike-Str-Advantage-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Great Strike - Glaive (Advantage)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a **Great Strike** Glaive attack at **Advantage** *&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[2d10!!cf<4cs>10kh1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[1d10!cf<0cs>100 [Great Strike]]] [Great Strike] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str] ]] [Str] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] + $[[1]] Slashing &#125;&#125;{{Dice Mods=$[[2]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[4]] Slashing + $[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[3]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125;
